      "name": "Sprint 8: Workflow Orchestrator Engine",
      "description": "Implement the server-side workflow execution engine that reads a saved workflow JSON schema, walks the node graph, executes Claude Managed Agent nodes using claude-opus-4-7, resolves inputMapping expressions, persists every step and event to the database, and updates run status throughout.",
      "priority": "high",
      "status": "completed",
